---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Tentang Saya" description="Senior Frontend Engineer based in Jakarta.">
    
    <!-- Wrapper Utama dengan Padding -->
    <div class="pt-10 md:pt-20">
        
        <!-- 1. HERO PROFILE SECTION -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-24">
            <!-- Kolom Teks -->
            <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 text-xs font-bold text-zinc-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-wider">
                    ðŸ‘‹ Halo, Saya idgo
                </div>
                <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 text-zinc-900 dark:text-white leading-[1.1]">
                    Bukan Sekadar <br> <span class="text-brand-500">Menulis Kode.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-lg">
                    Saya percaya bahwa kode yang bersih adalah bentuk seni, dan antarmuka yang baik adalah tentang empati terhadap pengguna.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                    <a href="https://wa.me/6281399721767" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-zinc-900 dark:bg-white text-white dark:text-zinc-950 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-lg">
                        <i class="ph-bold ph-paper-plane-tilt"></i> Hubungi Saya
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 text-zinc-900 dark:text-white border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-colors">
                        <i class="ph-bold ph-download-simple"></i> Unduh CV
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

           
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. BENTO GRID (STORY & TECH) -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-32">
            <!-- Story Card -->
            <div class="md:col-span-2 p-8 rounded-3xl bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800">
                <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-zinc-900 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2">
                    <i class="ph-fill ph-user-circle text-brand-500"></i> Cerita Saya
                </h3>
                <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
                    <p>
                        Hi! Saya engineer yang terobsesi dengan <strong>clean code</strong> dan <strong>user experience</strong>. Perjalanan saya dimulai dari rasa penasaran bagaimana sebuah piksel di layar bisa berinteraksi dengan manusia.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Saat ini saya fokus menggunakan stack modern seperti <strong>Astro</strong>, <strong>React</strong>, dan <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> untuk mengirimkan kode sesedikit mungkin ke browser user. Filosofi saya sederhana: <em>Make it work, make it right, make it fast.</em>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Tech Stack Card -->
            <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-brand-600 text-white flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden group">
                <div class="relative z-10">
                    <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i class="ph-fill ph-lightning"></i> Stack Utama
                    </h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 font-medium opacity-90">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><i class="ph-bold ph-check-circle"></i> JavaScript (ES6+)</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><i class="ph-bold ph-check-circle"></i> React & Next.js</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><i class="ph-bold ph-check-circle"></i> Astro Build</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><i class="ph-bold ph-check-circle"></i> Tailwind CSS</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><i class="ph-bold ph-check-circle"></i> TypeScript</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <!-- Dekorasi Icon Besar -->
                <i class="ph-fill ph-stack absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 text-9xl text-white opacity-10 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-500"></i>
            </div>
        </div>


<!-- 3. EXPERIENCE TIMELINE -->
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            Perjalanan Karir
        </h2>
        <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-brand-500 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative border-l-2 border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 ml-4 md:ml-0 space-y-12">

        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-0">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right md:absolute md:left-0 md:top-0">
                <span class="inline-block text-xs font-mono font-bold text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400 bg-brand-50 dark:bg-brand-900/20 px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 md:mb-0">
                    2021 - Sekarang
                </span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">
                    Founder & Product Engineer
                </h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-medium">
                    Kekondangan
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute left-[-9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-brand-600 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-zinc-950 shadow-sm"></div>

            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:ml-auto md:pl-12">
                <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-100 dark:border-zinc-800">
                    Membangun produk Kekondangan dari nol sebagai platform undangan digital & manajemen event.
                    Menangani end-to-end development mulai dari ide, UI/UX, frontend, backend, hingga deployment.
                    Fokus pada performa, pengalaman tamu, sistem QR invitation, dan dashboard event.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-0">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right md:absolute md:left-0 md:top-0">
                <span class="inline-block text-xs font-mono font-bold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 md:mb-0">
                    2019 - 2021
                </span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">
                    Web Developer / Creative Engineer
                </h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-medium">
                    IDGO & Project Agency
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute left-[-9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-zinc-300 dark:bg-zinc-700 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-zinc-950 shadow-sm"></div>

            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:ml-auto md:pl-12">
                <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-100 dark:border-zinc-800">
                    Mengerjakan berbagai project website company profile, landing page, dan sistem custom
                    untuk UMKM hingga brand menengah. Terbiasa mengubah desain menjadi implementasi nyata,
                    membangun layout responsif, animasi interaktif, serta berinteraksi langsung dengan klien.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 3 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-0">
            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right md:absolute md:left-0 md:top-0">
                <span class="inline-block text-xs font-mono font-bold text-zinc-400 bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-800 px-2 py-1 rounded mb-2 md:mb-0">
                    Sebelumnya
                </span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-zinc-900 dark:text-white">
                    Freelance Web Developer
                </h3>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-medium">
                    Independent Projects
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute left-[-9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-zinc-950 shadow-sm"></div>

            <div class="md:w-1/2 md:ml-auto md:pl-12">
                <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900/50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-zinc-100 dark:border-zinc-800">
                    Menerima berbagai project personal dan komunitas yang membentuk dasar problem solving,
                    kemandirian teknis, serta pemahaman bisnis digital dari sisi developer.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

</BaseLayout>